INTuitive Css Shortcuts (.intcs) is script for AutoHotkey (http://www.autohotkey.com/).
It lets you write css with less typing. For example if you
type in .boxs, it will be replaced with:
-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
-moz-box-shadow:    0px 0px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
box-shadow:         0px 0px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
This works in all editors and browsers.